  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dbb \u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d87\u0d9f\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Warnings from China to America based on Taiwan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China opposes any form of official relations between the US and the Taiwan region, and should expect resolute countermeasures in response to US provocations, said Liu Pengyu, a spokesman for the Chinese Embassy in the US.",
        "A fresh visit by a bipartisan US congressional delegation to Taiwan on Sunday shows the US does not want to see stability across the Taiwan Strait, described by the US as meddling in the internal affairs of both sides and China.",
        "\"The responsibility for the current tension across the Taiwan Strait rests entirely with the US side. They should bear all the consequences of the relevant lawmakers coming to Taiwan,\" he said."
      ],
